- SIMPLE TOUCH CONTROLS
Just touch anywhere on the screen to increase gravity and ROLL down hills. Let go at the top of the hill to FLY through the air.

- DASH
Not going to make it over a gap? just use two fingers to DASH forward and make the landing.

- POWER-UPS
Earn power-ups to make your donut FLY upwards, FLOAT in mid air, or get a instant BOOST of speed.

- BEAUTIFUL WORLDS
Experience 5 amazing worlds set in different locations to different music - 75 LEVELS AND COUNTING...
